Abraham Spencer of VA













		Replies: 0
	






						Abraham Spencer of VA
					

 kpape514
(View posts)




					Posted:	1197062965000


					Classification: Will


					Surnames: Spencer, Dickenson, Sharp






Hi,I believe that I descend from Abraham Spencer of Virginia.  Do you have information on that line?  Current on-line information indicates that he lived from 1735-1761 and married Lucy Dickerson or Dickenson, but I just got a copy of his will from the Albemarle County Courthouse and he had six children by the age of 25 and was wealthy enough to have 400 acres and some slaves.  That seems inconsisent to me! I wonder if this is in fact the older Abraham born in 1700 and perhaps he was married first to Susannah Sharp and second to Lucy Dickenson.  I will be happy to share info with you!  






















