ABRAHAM, SPENCER (A SENATOR FROM MICHIGAN)

ABRAHAM, SPENCER (a Senator from Michigan)

  Amendments
      Agriculture, rural development, FDA, and related agencies 
        programs: making appropriations (S. 1233), S7338 [21JN], 
        S10128 [3AU], S10197, S10255 [4AU]
      Bankruptcy: amend laws (S. 625), S14105, S14129, S14165, S14193 
        [5NO], S14261 [8NO]
      Budget: designation of emergencies (S. 557), S3944, S3945 [20AP]
      ------setting forth the Federal budget for 2000-2009 (S. Con. 
        Res. 20), S3177, S3197, S3280, S3281, S3285 [24MR], S3336, 
        S3341, S3346, S3347, S3348, S3351, S3373, S3524, S3527, S3528, 
        S3532, S3533, S3534, S3536 [25MR], S4090 [22AP]
      Computers: encourage expansion of electronic commerce (S. 761), 
